ess/article/3257225/chinese-education-giant-xj-international-hit-winding-petition-after-defaulting-us324-million-bond?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>华为2023年销量反弹9.63%，得益于Mate 60系列5G智能手机不受美国制裁的欢迎</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3257228/huawei-posts-963-cent-rebound-sales-2023-driven-popularity-mate-60-series-smartphones-defied-us?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>华为报告称，在其高端 Mate 60 系列 5G 智能手机强劲销售的推动下，2023 年销量增长出现反弹，该公司因芯片突破而继续面临美国的审查。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 08:45:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3257228/huawei-posts-963-cent-rebound-sales-2023-driven-popularity-mate-60-series-smartphones-defied-us?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>“没有明确的答案”：专家对间歇性禁食与心脏病死亡风险增加之间的联系的研究表示怀疑</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3256315/no-clear-answers-experts-cast-doubt-study-linking-intermittent-fasting-higher-risk-heart-disease?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>一项研究质疑限时饮食计划的长期影响。但专家表示，还需要进行更多研究。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 08:03:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3256315/no-clear-answers-experts-cast-doubt-study-linking-intermittent-fasting-higher-risk-heart-disease?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>尼日尔在遣散美军几天后与中国和俄罗斯“新朋友”打交道</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3257165/niger-cosies-new-friends-china-and-russia-just-days-after-sending-us-military-packing?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>在这个非洲国家发生重大外交转变后，北京将致力于扩大其石油和采矿业利益。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 08:00:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3257165/niger-cosies-new-friends-china-and-russia-just-days-after-sending-us-military-packing?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>万科老板承认2023年利润下滑面临“压力”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/business/china-business/article/3257182/china-vanke-boss-acknowledges-pressure-2023-profits-slump-amid-liquidity-distress-rumours?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>这家陷入困境的房地产开发商公布的 2023 年净利润下降了 46.4%，在该公司流动性问题的传言扰乱市场几周后，投资者感到震惊。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 04:33:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/business/china-business/article/3257182/china-vanke-boss-acknowledges-pressure-2023-profits-slump-amid-liquidity-distress-rumours?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>阿联酋王子与香港、习近平的政策转变、新加坡再次成为“亚洲最幸福国家”：《南华早报》本周七大亮点</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/week-asia/article/3257162/uae-prince-and-hong-kong-xis-policy-shift-singapore-asias-happiest-country-again-scmps-7-highlights?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>从迪拜王子推迟在香港开设家族办公室，到新加坡成为亚洲最幸福的国家，以下是《南华早报》最近报道的一些亮点。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 04:03:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/week-asia/article/3257162/uae-prince-and-hong-kong-xis-policy-shift-singapore-asias-happiest-country-again-scmps-7-highlights?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>民意调查显示，只有不到十分之三的美国人支持 TikTok 法案，该法案将迫使中国所有者出售该应用程序</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3257160/poll-shows-fewer-3-10-americans-support-tiktok-bill-would-force-chinese-owner-sell-app?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>一位调查分析师表示，年轻人——被视为总统选举结果的关键——尤其反对。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 04:01:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3257160/poll-shows-fewer-3-10-americans-support-tiktok-bill-would-force-chinese-owner-sell-app?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>随着科技巩固其支柱产业地位，中国5G市场将扩大，推动经济增长</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3257119/chinas-5g-market-set-expand-fuel-economic-growth-tech-solidifies-status-pillar-industry?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>尽管中国的5G市场和用户群已经是全球最大的，但最近的一项研究发现，随着技术发展成为长期增长的新引擎，该行业有望实现更大的增长。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 02:00:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3257119/chinas-5g-market-set-expand-fuel-economic-growth-tech-solidifies-status-pillar-industry?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>南海：北京敦促东南亚国家“珍惜和平”并帮助阻止紧张局势失控</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3257135/south-china-sea-beijing-urges-southeast-asian-nations-cherish-peace-and-help-stop-south-tensions?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>高级外交官刘振民告诉博鳌论坛，海南各国应在区域基础上解决争端，并警告外部人士不要“煽风点火”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 22:00:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3257135/south-china-sea-beijing-urges-southeast-asian-nations-cherish-peace-and-help-stop-south-tensions?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item></channel></rss>